<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>API Key Management System</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #3498db;
            --secondary-color: #2ecc71;
            --background-color: #ecf0f1;
            --text-color: #34495e;
            --header-color: #2c3e50;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: var(--text-color);
            background-color: var(--background-color);
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        header {
            background: var(--header-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding-top: 30px;
            min-height: 70px;
            border-bottom: var(--secondary-color) 3px solid;
        }
        header a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        header .branding {
            float: left;
        }
        header .branding h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        header nav {
            float: right;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        header .highlight, header .current a {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        header a:hover {
            color: var(--background-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .hero {
            min-height: 400px;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.7), rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.7)), url('https://source.unsplash.com/random/1600x900/?technology') no-repeat center center/cover;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            margin-top: 100px;
            font-size: 55px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        .button-light {
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        .button-light:hover {
            background: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }
        .features {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .box {
            float: left;
            width: 30%;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
        .box img {
            width: 90px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        footer {
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: var(--header-color);
            text-align: center;
        }
        #learn-more {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        #learn-more h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="branding">
                <h1><span class="highlight">API</span> Key Manager</h1>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/" class="current">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/signup">Sign Up</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/signin">Sign In</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Secure API Key Management</h1>
            <p>Streamline your API access control and enhance security with our powerful management system</p>
            <a href="/signup" class="button">Get Started</a>
            <a href="#learn-more" class="button button-light">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="learn-more" class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="box">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2885/2885417.png" alt="Security Icon">
                <h3>Enhanced Security</h3>
                <p>Protect your APIs with robust encryption and access controls, ensuring only authorized users can access your services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2620/2620503.png" alt="Key Rotation Icon">
                <h3>Easy Key Rotation</h3>
                <p>Regularly update and rotate API keys with just a few clicks, maintaining the highest level of security for your systems.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2885/2885417.png" alt="Permissions Icon">
                <h3>Granular Permissions</h3>
                <p>Set specific permissions and access levels for each API key, giving you complete control over your API ecosystem.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="learn-more">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>What is API Key Management?</h2>
            <p>API key management is a crucial aspect of modern software development that allows you to control and monitor access to your APIs. It provides a secure way to authenticate and authorize users or applications, track usage patterns, and gather valuable insights about how your APIs are being utilized.</p>
            <p>With our API Key Management System, you can enhance security, easily rotate keys, and set granular permissions, giving you complete control over your API ecosystem.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 <a href="https://github.com/Arnab-m1">Arnab</a>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
